    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and roughly chop the<strong> shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Peel and roughly chop the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>red chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Chop the<strong> lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half</p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks, keeping the leaves and stalks separate</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
